- Add new z-order commands (`raise_window`, `lower_window`) in the same capability/dispatch blocks: `app/command_registry.cpp:188`, `app/command_registry.cpp:190`, `app/command_registry.cpp:709`.
- `move_window`, `resize_window`, `close_window` do not inherently need z-awareness.
